                <div class="fp-list__item-text">
                    <h3>Queen&#39;s Hospital Close</h3>

<p>Located on Bath Row, just a 20-minute walk to City South Campus and less than a mile from the Bull Ring shopping and City Centre restaurants and bars.</p>                    <a class="text-cta--primary" href="/student-info/accommodation/halls/queens-hospital-close" target="_self">More on Queen's Hospital</a>                </div>
