                        <h2 class="panel__heading">Living in halls</h2>

<p><span>We realise that moving in with complete strangers can be daunting. But living at uni is also incredibly exciting, the chance to meet new people and make new friends should be seen as a positive. Here's some tips and advice on making the move.</span></p>
                            <div class="panel__ctas">
                                <a class="button--primary" href="/student-info/accommodation/living-in-halls" target="_self">Living in halls</a>
                            </div>
                    </div>

